402
00:35:27,290 --> 00:35:28,511
Rapunzel

403
00:35:36,026 --> 00:35:39,758
Rapunzel, 把头发放下来

404
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:43,217
Rapunzel?

405
00:36:02,812 --> 00:36:03,709
Rapunzel

406
00:36:06,772 --> 00:36:08,459
Rapunzel

407
00:36:52,857 --> 00:36:56,108
就在这附近哪里了

408
00:36:56,866 --> 00:36:58,783
